name: Joli.js Sample
body:
### Joli.js Sample

This is a sample project of Joli.js, an ORM for Titanium Mobile DB.
Please import whole project into Titanium Studio and execute 'build'. 

Enjoy!
tagline: This is a sample project of Joli.js, an ORM for Titanim Mobile DB.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
